Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.47,0:00:32.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker  把她捏碎了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.86,0:02:23.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.60,0:02:25.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker  快点干掉她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.00,0:02:30.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.22,0:02:47.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,混…混账
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她放开
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.15,0:02:51.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.52,0:03:01.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.88,0:03:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经够了  快点离开  Master
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.19,0:03:09.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把她放开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.31,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不…不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.54,0:03:32.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别使用这招  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为…为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.05,0:03:45.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,除此之外…别无选择了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.72,0:03:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是解开结界就这副样子了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.98,0:03:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,现在的你无法使用这把剑
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.14,0:03:54.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以等着我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:57.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果是在现实中敌不过的对手
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.30,0:03:59.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就去幻想能赢得了的武器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.57,0:04:04.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由我来制造
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.71,0:04:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能做到的  也仅限于此了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.35,0:04:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就由我来准备…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.19,0:04:28.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你所使用的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:45.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那把剑是  我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.01,0:05:09.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再来一次
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.33,0:05:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原本不应该破碎的剑之所以会破碎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.88,0:05:13.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因为我的想象有破绽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,投影  开始
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:16.18,pos,NTP,0,0,0,,Trace, on
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.51,0:05:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我应该挑战的是我自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.54,0:05:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能有一丝的差错与妥协
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.93,0:05:30.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想定基本构造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.19,0:05:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,复制构成材质
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.03,0:05:40.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,重现累积年月
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.56,0:05:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,凌驾  完成诸多工程
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.25,0:05:50.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,于此  幻想凝聚成剑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.06,0:06:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.04,0:06:08.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哼  明明不可能赢过Berserker的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:13.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,都已经制造出超越Berserker的剑了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.55,0:06:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我却没办法使用吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.43,0:06:29.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎  把手给我
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.15,0:07:42.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是你的剑吗  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是Caliburn  选定国王的石中剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.36,0:07:47.05,up,NTP,0,0,0,,Caliburn：必胜黄金之剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.47,0:07:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是我永远失去了的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.18,0:07:54.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,毕竟只是那个男人制造出来的幻想
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.42,0:07:57.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不可能再次存在的剑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:03.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然而  这份幻想也不可小看
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:06.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居然仅以普通的一击
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.55,0:08:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就毁灭了我的身体七次
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.85,0:08:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,士郎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.68,0:08:26.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.09,0:08:30.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,骗人…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.12,0:08:33.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Berserker
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.89,0:08:35.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.41,0:08:39.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以  Saber
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.32,0:08:42.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请不要对伊莉雅下手
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.20,0:08:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,既然Berserker已经不存在了  那伊莉雅…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.84,0:09:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你醒了啊  士郎
